show.description: Marriage, Lord Pei is a clingy person-In this story of unexpected romance, Lord Pei’s unwavering devotion wraps around his beloved like a warm but unshakable embrace. No matter the storms or silences, his clinginess becomes both her greatest comfort and her sweetest dilemma.
